<HEAD>
<TITLE>Microscopy UK / MICSCAPE - 3D Stereo Microscopy : Insects</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#000000" text="#00ff00">

<a name="top">

<P>
<center><h1>3d Image: Cockroach</h1></center>
<p>

<center><IMG SRC="3dcock3b.jpg"></center>
<p>
<h4>
This is the little creature which would probably rule our cities along with the rats
if a tragic catastrophic incident wiped out civilization tomorrow. The cockroach is 
one on the fastest insects, and as seen here, loves our salads and other foods
(meat) as muchas we do.
<p>
This images was created from video footage shot at London (Regents Park) Zoo, where 
the insect house contains an area layed out with a dinner table crawling with 
cockroaches. Better than any horror movie! 
</h4>
