<TITLE>Microscopy UK / MICSCAPE - 3D Stereo Microscopy : Micro-fossils</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#000000" text="#00ff00">

<a name="top">

<P>
<center><h1>3D Gastropods </h1></center>
<p>

<center><IMG SRC="3dshell.jpg"></center>
<h4>
The actual size of this micro-fossil is smaller than this letter: X.
You are looking at the remaining relic of the home of a sea-snail or
Gastropod. It lived over 50 million years ago. Magnified here at over 400x, you 
can see the shell casing has been damaged. 
</h4>


