<TITLE>Microscopy UK / MICSCAPE - 3D Stereo Microscopy : Syringe</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#000000" text="#00ff00">

<a name="top">

<P>
<center><h1>3D Syringe</h1></center>
<p>

<center><IMG SRC="3dnd.jpg"></center>
<p>
<h4>
This syringe has been used! To the naked eye it looks extremely
sharp, but here at 100x magnification (greater depending on monitor
size), you can see how the tip has been buckled during use.
<p>
A tiny drop of liquid still remains in the hollow shaft. 
</h4>
