<DOCNO>WT24-B19-39</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000332-B011-151</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk:80/mag/articles/ellspon.html 194.88.132.107 19970115053303 text/html 5715
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 05:39:07 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
