<B>Key</B><BR>
ad - adhesive disc<BR>
an - anus<BR>
as - ascending branch of the digestive system<BR>
cc - compound cilia<BR>
ce - ciliated epidermis<BR>
co - constriction (or 'neck')<BR>
de - descending branch of the digestive system<BR>
ep - epidermis<BR>
ga - ganglion<BR>
gl - gut lining cell<BR>
ib - inner bud<BR>
mc - myoepithelial cell<BR>
mr - mouth ring<BR>
ne - nerve<BR>
p1 - penis 1<BR>
p2 - penis 2<BR>
sc - stomach cells<BR>
sp - sperm<BR>
s1 - sphincter 1<BR>
