<BLOCKQUOTE><A HREF="JTO/JTdesc.html">Join Together Online</A> is a resource center and meeting place for

communities working to reduce the harms associated with the use of illicit

drugs, excessive alcohol and tobacco.</BLOCKQUOTE>



