	</TD>
	
<TD WIDTH="40%"  VALIGN="CENTER">
<CENTER>
<FONT  COLOR="RED">SPECIAL REPORT:</FONT><BR>
<H3>Follow the Money</FONT></H3></CENTER>

<FONT SIZE="-1">Federal funding for substance abuse treatment and prevention does not begin and end with the <A HREF="http://www.samhsa.gov/">SAMHSA</A>. In fact, more than a dozen federal agencies share in over $4.5 billion in drug demand reduction funding.</FONT><P>


<B>Follow the story:</B> 

<FONT SIZE="-1"><UL TYPE=1 START="1">
	



<LI><IMG SRC = "/gif/new.gif" WIDTH="23" HEIGHT="12" ALT = "New!"><A HREF="/posting/FundingNews.qry?function=detail&FundingNews_Aid=635">The Federal Drug and Alcohol Abuse Budget </A>


<LI><A HREF="/posting/FundingNews.qry?function=detail&FundingNews_Aid=538">SAPT Block Grant</A>



<LI><A HREF="/posting/FundingNews.qry?function=detail&FundingNews_Aid=530">Tapping Into Entitlements</A>
