<H2><CENTER>Public Policy </CENTER>
</H2>

<TABLE WIDTH="100%" CELLPADDING=2>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="CENTER">


<A HREF="/news/alerts/Latest_News.qry?MediaAction=True&Summaries=On&Max=7&Last=30"><B>Alerts</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Watch here for important announcements relating to national and local public
policy. If you are interested in posting an Alert, send email to <A HREF="mailto:info@jointogether.org">info@jointogether.org</A>.</FONT><BR>
<BR>

<A HREF="panel.html"><B>Policy Panels</B></A> <BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Join Together sponsors public policy panels to address issues communities
identify as barriers to their success.</FONT><BR>
<BR>
<A HREF="surveys.html"><B>Surveys</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Join Together conducts surveys to describe community activity and to assess
the contributions and needs of community organizations and coalitions. Other
surveys relating to substance abuse trends will also be found here.</FONT><BR>
<BR>

<A HREF="/go.qry?gopher://gopher.igc.apc.org:7003/11/pol"><B>Archives</B></A><BR>
