<H3><A HREF="/fellows/fellowtable.qry?function=form">Meet the Join Together<BR>
National Fellows</A></H3> 

The Join Together National Fellows Program recognizes community leaders
who have made significant contributions toward reducing the harm from substance
abuse and who have potential to provide long-term leadership. Here, in this
searchable database, you can meet these 132 community leaders. </P>

