al initiative to survive in a court of law. Just recently, President Clinton's drug czar, Barry McCaffrey, denounced the proposition as a "hoax" and said the federal government would not hold back on prosecuting doctors who prescribe the drug. <br><br>

<b>Hot Links to Prop 215 Information:</b>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://Vote96.ss.ca.gov/Vote96/cgi/mapprop-215.map?60,15">View a map of the returns</A> <LI>read the <A HREF="http://Vote96.ss.ca.gov/Vote96/html/BP/215text.htm">text of the Proposition</A><LI>follow <A HREF="http://Vote96.ss.ca.gov/Vote96/html/BP/215.htm">arguments for and against</A> it</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE><FONT SIZE = "-1"><TABLE WIDTH ="100%"><TR><TD WIDTH="30%"><B>Date:   </B>11/06/1996</TD><TD ALIGN="RIGHT"><b>Source: Join Together Online</TD></TR></TABLE></FONT><P><I>Distributed by <A HREF="http://www.jointogether.org">Join Together Online</A>.</I></P>    <P><CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/footer.map"><IMG SRC="/MapServe/footer.gif"WIDTH="441" HEIGHT="27" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle  ISMAP></A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/default.html">JTO</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/index.html">Index</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/search.html">Search</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/comments.html">Comments</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/help.html">Help</A></FONT><BR><BR><HR><FONT SIZE="-1">Distributed by Join Together<BR><A HREF="/">http://www.jointogether.org</A></FONT></B></CENTER></BODY></HTML><!-- 57 tics elapsed -->
