    <HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE>News Summaries</TITLE></HEAD><!-Default-><BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/newsban.map">	<IMG SRC="/MapServe/newsban.gif" WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="75" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle ISMAP></A><BR><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/jto/news/news.html"><BR>News &amp; Communications</A> | <A HREF="/news/jto/Latest_News.qry?Illicit=True&Alcohol=True&Tobacco=True&General=True">News</A> | <A HREF="/news/releases/Latest_News.qry?PressReleases=True&Summaries=On&Max=7&Last=30">Releases</A>| <A HREF="gopher://gopher.igc.apc.org:7003/11/news">Archives</A> | <A HREF="/URLs/JTO/URL_Show.qry?header=news&filter=drugs&Category=Media&Summaries=on">Links</A></FONT><BR></CENTER><p><TABLE WIDTH = "90%" CELLSPACING = "0"><TR><TD WIDTH = "60%"><h2>THC Cancer Study</h2></TD><TD></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN = "2"><FONT COLOR = "BLACK">A federal study has concluded that the main ingredient in marijuana does not cause cancer in laboratory animals, the Associated Press reported Jan. 30. The latest findings call into question the long-held contention by the federal government that marijuana is carcinogenic.<br><br>According to the $2 million study, high doses of the main ingredient in marijuana -- tetrahydrocannabinol, or THC -- were put into the stomachs of mice and rats daily for a two-year period. "We found absolutely no evidence of cancer," said John Bucher, deputy director of the National Toxicology Program.<br><br>Although the study's results concluded THC does not cause cancer in laboratory animals, the animals were not exposed to marijuana smoke; therefore, the potential of inhaled marijuana was not examined. The Federal Drug Administration, the National Cancer Institute and other federal agencies were in charge of overseeing the study. <br><br></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE><FONT SIZE = "-1"><TABLE WIDTH ="100%"><TR><TD WIDTH="30%"><B>Date:   </B>01/30/1997</TD><TD ALIGN="RIGHT"><b>Source: Join Together Online</TD></TR></TABLE></FONT><P><I>Distributed by <A HREF="http://www.jointogether.org">Join Together Online</A>.</I></P>    <P><CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/footer.map"><IMG SRC="/MapServe/footer.gif"WIDTH="441" HEIGHT="27" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle  ISMAP></A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/default.html">JTO</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/index.html">Index</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/search.html">Search</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/comments.html">Comments</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/help.html">Help</A></FONT><BR><BR><HR><FONT SIZE="-1">Distributed by Join Together<BR><A HREF="/">http://www.jointogether.org</A></FONT></B></CENTER></BODY></HTML><!-- 46 tics elapsed -->
