<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Help</TITLE>
</HEAD>
	<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">




<table cellspacing="17">
<tr><td><!--    --></td><td> 
<IMG SRC="../gif/jtoheaderSmall.gif" align=center>
</td><td>
<IMG SRC="../gif/help.gif" ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="75" HEIGHT="25">
</td></tr>
</table>



<table cellspacing="17">
<tr><td><!--    --></td><td> 

<H3>Welcome!</H3>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Like any good Web site, we are always "under construction".
It is our hope
that this Web site develops into a place where communities fighting substance
abuse come to work and interact with each other. To reach this goal, we
need to build this site in cooperation with YOU! <A HREF="comments.html">Let
us know what you think</A>.</FONT>
<BR><BR>



<BR>
<H3>Navigation</H3>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Each page has a graphical Header and Footer. These graphics will let you know
where in the site you are and allow you to click around to navigate. If
you have a slow connection to the Internet, you can still navigate easily with graphic loading in your browser turned off.  The <B><A HREF="/JTO/index.html">Index</A></B> is a tool to easily
see the outline of our site and navigate quickily through different levels.<BR>
</FONT><BR>

<H3>Shortcuts</H3>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Once you're acquainted with Join Together Online, you'll discover the features you'll come back for again and again.  Use the Shortcuts drop-down menu on our home page to quickly access several popular destinations, eliminating the need to enter a certain section of the web site first.</FONT><BR><BR>


</td><td>

<H3>Online Service Access</H3>
<FONT SIZE="-1">To get the fastest access to JTO, or any other Web site, you need a direct, SLIP or PPP-type connection to the Internet from your computer.  Online services not offering this connection only provide indirect Internet access, often producing frustrating delays in retrieving Web pages.
<BR><BR>
America Online, a popular online service, does not presently offer this type of direct Internet connection.  Although you don't get the propietary, organized content of an online service, a SLIP or PPP account with an Internet Service Provider will give you the most efficient access to the Web.  <BR><BR>

<IMG SRC="/gif/new.gif" ALIGN=LEFT>If you need help finding such a provider, consult our online recommendations for <A HREF="/jto/help/best_win.html">Windows </A> and <A HREF="/jto/help/best_mac.html">Macintosh</A> users. Or, see our table of <A HREF="/jto/help/isptable.html">national ISPs</A>.  If you're still stumped, <A HREF="mailto:info@jointogether.org">write us</A> for help.</FONT>

<BR><BR>
<H3>Web Browsers</H3>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Like many other Web publishers, we suggest you use <A HREF="http://www.netscape.com">Netscape Navigator</A> or <A HREF="http://www.microsoft.com/ie/msie.htm">Microsoft Internet Explorer</A> to browse our site. These browsers operate easily and efficiently and will allow you the best, most reliable access to Join Together Online. We are designing more and more of our site to comply with Netscape formatting standards, supported in Netscape' browser as well as in Internet Explorer. Both browsers are available for free and may be downloaded from their links above.</FONT><BR><BR>
</td></tr>
</table>

