<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Events Calendar</TITLE>
</HEAD>
	<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/community.map"><IMG SRC="/Mapserve/community.gif"WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="75" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle ISMAP></A><BR><P></A><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/jto/community/community.html">Community Action</A> | <A HREF="calendar.html">Events</A>| <A HREF="/jto/community/resource.html">Resource Center</A> | <A HREF="/jto/community/treatment.html">Treatment</A> | <A HREF="/jto/community/comex.html">COMEX</A>| <A HREF="/jto/forum/jtolink/links.html">Links</A></CENTER></FONT>
<CENTER><H2>Events Calendar
</H2></CENTER>

<BLOCKQUOTE><FONT SIZE="-1">We have developed this <B>Events Calendar</B> so that anyone in the nation
wishing to <B>find</B> or <B>post</B> a substance abuse related event may
do so quickly and easily. By entering in your own data or searching the
database by topic, place, date or event, this one tool can serve the needs
of small towns and national organizations.<BR>
<BR>
This will only be a valuable resource if YOU use it.</FONT><BR>
<BR>
<B>







<a HREF="/query/e_search.qry?function=form">Search the Calendar</a> 
</B><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">The <B>Events Calendar</B> can be searched in a variety of ways. Searching
by tobacco, for instance, will yield a list of all tobacco related events
nationally. Adding a search for State will narrow the search down to tobacco
related events in that state only.<BR>
<BR>
Even if you just want to post an event, we urge you to search the database
<B>first</B> to make sure that your event has not already been posted by
someone else. </FONT><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="/query/calendar_post.qry?function=form">Add an Event to the
Calendar</A></B><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Before posting an event, please search the database to insure that it has
not already been posted by someone else. You may copy and paste from your
word processor into these fields. For best results though, save your file
as text with hard carriage returns first.<BR></FONT></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>

<CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/footer.map"><IMG SRC="/Mapserve/footer.gif"  WIDTH="441" HEIGHT="27" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle ISMAP></A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/default.html">JTO</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/index.html">Index</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/search.html">Search</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/comments.html">Comments</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/help.html">Help</A><BR><BR><HR>Distributed by Join Together<BR><A HREF="http://www.jointogether.org">http://www.jointogether.org</A></FONT></CENTER>
</BODY>
</HTML>
