<H2><CENTER>National Forum</CENTER>
</H2>
<BLOCKQUOTE><B><A HREF="coffee.html">The Coffee House<BR></A></B>
<FONT SIZE="-1">The nation's pressing substance abuse problems can't be solved by reading alone! Use the Web to its fullest extent -- join with others around the nation who are discussing the tough issues facing us.</FONT><BR>
<BR>



<B><A HREF="/jto/forum/lists/email.html">Electronic Mail Discussion
Lists</A></B><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Interact with your colleagues across the nation and the world using Internet email lists. Learn about Subabuse, Join Together's national email list for substance abuse professionals, and many other related lists.</FONT><BR>
<BR>

