<H2>Coming Soon!</H2>
</CENTER><B>JTO Link</B>, a searchable directory of Internet sites related to
substance abuse, will be coming online very shortly. You'll be able to locate
sites by category or by keyword search.  We're desigining a Yahoo-like
interface for this unique database that will help you locate related sites
quickly and easily.   <BR><BR>
Because JTO Link will soon be ready, we've temporarily stopped posting new URLs
to the various links pages throughout Join Together Online.  If you've recently
requested a link to your site on JTO, it will be processed for inclusion in the
new database.  Stay tuned! <BR><BR>
