<DOCNO>WT24-B19-133</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000694-B037-306</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www2.quitnet.org:80/jto/issues/tx&crime/fact.html 192.12.191.21 19970210001037 text/html 5107
