<DOCNO>WT24-B19-156</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000694-B039-243</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www2.quitnet.org:80/jto/issues/inhalants/Action_steps.html 192.12.191.21 19970210001458 text/html 4433
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
