<BLOCKQUOTE><B>We Want to Hear From You!</B><BR>
Our goal is to create an interactive online space where communities around
the United States can find the information and assistance they need to be
more effective in their fight against substance abuse. <BR>
<BR>
As we develop this Web site, we want and need your comments: 

<UL>
<LI>What works?<BR>
<LI>What doesn't? <BR>
<LI>What's missing? <BR>
<LI>What's valuable? 
</UL>

We have created a discussion area for this purpose in the <A HREF="../../conf/login.qry?function%3Dform">Coffee
House</A>. If you prefer to email us, you may direct your comments to <A HREF="mailto:info@jointogether.org">info@jointogether.org</A>.<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

