<HEAD>
    <TITLE>The Fact Is...</TITLE>
</HEAD>
	<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF"><IMG SRC="coverSmall.gif" WIDTH="94" HEIGHT="121" ALIGN=left NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3">
<CENTER><H2>FIXING A FAILING SYSTEM</H2>
<H3>NATIONAL POLICY RECOMMENDATIONS: <BR>
How the Criminal Justice System Should Work with Communities to Reduce Substance
Abuse</H3><P>
<A HREF="Forward.html">Forward</A> | <A HREF="members.html">Members</A> | Fact
Is | 
<A HREF="intro.html">Intro</A> | <A HREF="fixing.html">Fixing A Failing
System</A> |<BR>
<A HREF="rec1.html">Rec. 1 </A>| <A HREF="rec2.html">Rec. 2 </A>| <A HREF="rec3.html">Rec.
3</A> | <A HREF="rec4.html">Rec. 4 </A>| <A HREF="rec5.html">Rec. 5 </A>|
<A HREF="rec6.html">Rec. 6</A><BR>
<A HREF="conclustion.html">Conclusion</A> | <A HREF="resources.html">Resources</A>
| <A HREF="bib.html">Bibliography</A></CENTER>

<P><BR>
<H3>THE FACT IS...</H3>

<H4>The number of incarcerated drug offenders has risen by 510% from 1983
to 1993. </H4>
<BLOCKQUOTE>Source: Marc Mauer, Young Black Americans and the Criminal Justice
System: Five Years Later. The Sentencing Project. 1995.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<hr>
<H4>The number of drug arrests tripled during the 1980's -- from 471,000
in 1980 to 1,247,000 in 1989. </H4>
<BLOCKQUOTE>Source: Bureau of Justice Statistics &quot;Drugs and Crime Facts&quot;
1990</BLOCKQUOTE><hr>
<H4>The total adult population on probation or parole needing alcohol or
drug treatment is 1.6 million (55%).</H4>
<BLOCKQUOTE>Source: Bureau of Justice StatisticsPPress Release 1995</BLOCKQUOTE><hr>
<H4>In August, 1995, the Bureau of Justice Assistance reported that drug
courts, diverting nonviolent defendants from jail time to treatment, could
lower the recidivism rate, increase successful treatment outcomes, and save
tax payers $5,000 per defendant in jail costs alone. </H4>
<BLOCKQUOTE>Source: U.S. Department of Justice </BLOCKQUOTE>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/footer.map"><IMG SRC="/Mapserve/footer.gif"  WIDTH="441" HEIGHT="27" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle ISMAP></A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/default.html">JTO</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/index.html">Index</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/search.html">Search</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/comments.html">Comments</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/help.html">Help</A><BR><BR><HR>Distributed by Join Together<BR><A HREF="http://www.jointogether.org">http://www.jointogether.org</A></FONT></CENTER>
</BODY>
