<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000694-B044-175</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www2.quitnet.org:80/jto/issues/Inhalants/others.html 192.12.191.21 19970210002725 text/html 3452
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
