<H2><CENTER>Subscribing to Subabuse</CENTER>
</H2>


You may request a subscription by sending email to <A
HREF="mailto:info@jointogether.org">info@jointogether.org</A> with the following information:
<UL>
	<LI>your name
	<LI>organization
	<LI>street address, state and zip code
	<LI>phone and fax number
	<LI>email address
	<LI>a brief description of your work as it relates to substance abuse
</UL>

To be considered for a subscription to Subabuse, you must provide information for all categories that are applicable
to you. We use your address and contact information for geographical
user statistics.  You will receive an email reply within 3 days regarding your subscription. <BR>

<BR>
<CENTER><I>Thanks for your interest!</I></CENTER>


