<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Inhalant Abuse</TITLE>
</HEAD>
	<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/issues.map"><IMGSRC="/Mapserve/issues.gif"WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="75" BORDER="0 ALIGN=middle"ISMAP ALIGN=bottom></A></CENTER>
<H2><CENTER>Inhalant Abuse</CENTER>
</H2>
When we think of drugs, most of us think of marijuana, heroine and cocaine.
But today, the new drugs of choice for some kids are common -- but often
deadly -- household substances such as white out, glue and paint. This Hot
Issue Action Kit focuses on this rising problem. We suggest you use this
material to raise public awareness in March, which is National Inhalant
Awareness Month. We especially encourage you to reach out to youth who have
dropped out of school and may not be aware of the dangers associated with
inhalants.<BR>
<BR>
To get this message out to the public and key groups in your community,
we have provided you with the following:
<UL>
<LI>An <A HREF="overview.html">Overview </A> outlining Inhalants and how
they are commonly abused;<BR>
<BR>
<LI>A list of <A HREF="Warning.html">Warning Signs</A> of Inhalant abuse
to help others recognize when someone may be using household products to
get high;<BR>
<BR>
<LI>A <A HREF="Inhalant_Facts.html">Fact Sheet</A> summarizing the research
on the dangers of Inhalant abuse and national trends of this problem among
youth;<BR>
<BR>
<LI>Concrete <A HREF="Action_steps.html">Action Steps</A> you can take to
address Inhalant abuse in <B>your</B> community, and profiles of <A HREF="others.html">What
Others Have Done</A> in their communities.<BR>
<BR>
<LI>Sample <A HREF="letter.html">Letter to the Editor</A> and <A HREF="oped.html">Op-Ed</A>
piece you can tailor to fit your community and then submit to your local
newspaper for publication. 
</UL>
We would like to know if these tools are helpful and if you have attracted
media attention for your efforts. Please give us your feedback and any suggestions
for improving Hot Issues. You can call <A HREF="mailto:diane@jointogether.org">Diane
Barry</A> or <A HREF="mailto:lisa@jointogether.org">Lisa Falk</A> at Join
Together: (617) 437-1500 or fax us a note at (617) 437-9394. <BR>
<BR>
