<HEAD>

<TITLE>PSA's</TITLE>


</HEAD>
	<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/issues.map"><IMGSRC="/Mapserve/issues.gif"WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="75" BORDER="0 ALIGN=middle"ISMAP ALIGN=bottom></A></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

<H2>Radio Public Service Announcements</H2>
</CENTER>
<I>You can adapt any or all of the following 30-second Public Service Announcements for use on local radio stations.</I> 
<P>
<B>Directions:</B> Type each script double-spaced on your letterhead with the name and phone number of a contact person at
your organization. Try sending different scripts to public service directors at different stations. Follow up by
calling to see if each station will run these ads. Send a thank you note to the manager of any station that airs one
of your PSAs.
<BR
<BR>
<BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) wants parents to know that if your kids
are under the age of 21 and they're drinking, then they're doing drugs. For more information on how you can draw the
line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call (INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE
NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) is sounding a wake-up call by telling our
community that bars and stores that sell booze to minors are pushing the illegal drug that does the most damage. For
more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call (INSERT YOUR
PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that nearly half of all
college students who have been the victim of a crime had been drinking before the crime occurred. For more
information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call (INSERT YOUR PHONE
NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that alcohol is the deadliest
drug for America's teenagers: a 16-year-old is more likely to die from a drinking-related problem than any other
cause. For more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call
(INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that drinking is associated
with the leading causes of death among young people, including car crashes, murder and suicide. For more information
on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call (INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER).
That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).

<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that the vast majority of
students don't know that a standard mixed drink, a glass of table wine and a can of beer all contain the same amount
of alcohol. For more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA),
call (INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) asks you to remember that many young
people don't know that if you drink too much and too quickly you can die from an overdose of alcohol. For more
information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call (INSERT YOUR PHONE
NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that despite the legal
drinking age of 21, high school students still consume 31 million gallons of wine coolers and 102 million gallons of
beer each year. For more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA),
call (INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that even though most
teenagers know you should not drink and drive, nearly a third still accept rides from drivers who have been drinking.
For more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA), call (INSERT
YOUR PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) reminds you that nearly two-thirds of
teenagers who drink -- including those as young as 12 or 13-- report that they can walk into a store and buy their
own alcoholic beverages. For more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF
YOUR AREA), call (INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
April is Alcohol Awareness Month and the (INSERT NAME OF YOUR ORGANIZATION) asks you to consider this: college
students consume more beer than soft drinks and studies have shown that the more they drink, the lower their grade
point average. For more information on how you can draw the line at underage drinking in (INSERT NAME OF YOUR AREA),
call (INSERT YOUR PHONE NUMBER). That's (REPEAT PHONE NUMBER).
<BR><BR>
<CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/footer.map"><IMG SRC="/Mapserve/footer.gif"  WIDTH="441" HEIGHT="27" BORDER="0" ALIGN=middle ISMAP></A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE="-1"><A HREF="/default.html">JTO</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/index.html">Index</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/search.html">Search</A> | <A HREF="/JTO/comments.html">Comments</A>| <A HREF="/JTO/help.html">Help</A><BR><BR><HR>Distributed by Join Together<BR><A HREF="http://www.jointogether.org">http://www.jointogether.org</A></FONT></CENTER>
