<TITLE>Sample Op-Ed Cover Letter</TITLE>
</HEAD>


	<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">

<CENTER><A HREF="/Mapserve/issues.map"><IMGSRC="/Mapserve/issues.gif"WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="75" BORDER="0 ALIGN=middle"ISMAP ALIGN=bottom></A></CENTER>


<BR>


<H3>Drinking and Driving</H3>
<H2>Sample Op-Ed Cover Letter</H2></center>
<br>
If you wish, you can generate a ready to print letter by filling in the form boxes and pressing [Generate] at the bottom.

<HR>

<P>

<FORM ACTION="Alcohol_PitchOutput.nclk" METHOD=POST>


<P>
Dear <INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="Reporter" VALUE="Editor" SIZE=35>:<p>


<P>Each holiday season, lives are tragically lost as the result of fatal drunk driving crashes.
You can help prevent more residents of our community from becoming a statistic by helping to raise public awareness about the dangers of drinking and driving.


<P>Enclosed is an Op-Ed alerting readers to the problem of drinking and driving and to urge them to support lower legal Blood Alcohol Content levels in our state, which have been proven to save lives. In addition, the Op-Ed provides them with some concrete steps they can take -- such as educating themselves and others about the dangers of drunk driving, becoming responsible drivers and responsible party hosts, and encouraging parents not to provide alcohol to minors. 


<P>Please feel free to call me at <INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="Phone" VALUE="Phone number"> if you need help getting in touch with some local prevention programs.<p>

<P>Thank you for helping to make our streets and highways safer for everyone.

<P>Sincerely,
<p>

<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="Name" VALUE="Your name" size =35><br>
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="Title" VALUE="Your Title"><br>
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="Organization" VALUE="Your Organization" SIZE=30><br>
<br>

<p><BR><HR>
