<DOCNO>WT24-B19-435</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA034-000684-B042-106</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www2.quitnet.org:80/news/releases/Show_News.qry?News_uid=9787 192.12.191.21 19970209205229 text/html 6847
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
